             person("Wenzel", "Hans-Georg", role = "ctb"))
Maintainer: Jonathan Kennel <jkennel@uoguelph.ca>
Description: This is a port of Fortran 'ETERNA 3.4' code <http://igets.u-strasbg.fr/soft_and_tool.php> 
             for calculating synthetic Earth tides.
